<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.1.9">
<l>tūyāy cuṭarmā matipōluyirk kellām</l>
<l>tāyā yaḷikkiṉ ṟataṇṭāmaraik kaṇṇā</l>
<l>vāyā valainī rulakēḻumuṉ ṉuṇṭa</l>
<l>vāyā vuṉṉaiyeṅ ṅaṉamnāṉmaṟak kēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You of purity like the great, bright moon, [you] with cool lotus eyes</l>
<l>Who cares for all creatures as a mother,</l>
<l>You whose mouth once devoured the seven worlds with tossing waters,</l>
<l>Herder, how [would] I forget you?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
